<h2>scotland.computer</h2>
<p><p>An instance of the Mastodon social network for the tech/startup scene in Scotland.</p>

<p>The goal is to gather all the web/tech people in one place to make for an interesting local timeline.</p>

<p>You don't need to actually be Scottish or in Scotland! Friends, the curious, and all of good will are welcome!</p></p>
